OL,3,CWhat are the changes being made to
OL,4,Cdriving tests?
OL,6,FFrom April 8, the Driver and Vehicle
OL,7,FStandards Agency (DVSA) will require
OL,8,Flearner drivers to give ten full
OL,9,Fworking days' notice to change or
OL,10,Fcancel their car driving test without
OL,11,Flosing the test fee.
OL,13,FCurrently learner drivers need to give
OL,14,Fthree full working days notice to
OL,15,Favoid losing the fee, with Sundays and
OL,16,Fpublic holidays not counting.
