OL,3,CWhat are the changes being made to
OL,4,Cdriving tests?
OL,6,FThe new rule only applies to car
OL,7,Fdriving tests, whilst all other
OL,8,Fvehicles as well as theory tests will
OL,9,Fstill only require three days notice
OL,10,Fto cancel.
