OL,3,CWhat are the changes being made to
OL,4,Cdriving tests?
OL,6,FAccording to the government, about
OL,7,F60,000 test appointments were wasted
OL,8,Fin 2024 because people failed to show
OL,9,Fup.
OL,11,FThe DVSA is urging learners to cancel
OL,12,Ftheir tests if they know they won't be
OL,13,Fable to make it instead of just not
OL,14,Fshowing up.
