OL,3,CWhat are the changes being made to
OL,4,Cdriving tests?
OL,6,FThe DVSA will be emailing all learner
OL,7,Fdrivers to let them know about this
OL,8,Fchange. From April 8, when the changes
OL,9,Fwill be implemented, the new ten-day
OL,10,Fdeadline will be shown when they check
OL,11,Fthe details of their test online.
OL,13,FLearners who've had to cancel at short
OL,14,Fnotice due to an illness, bereavement
OL,15,Fwill still be able to apply for a
OL,16,Frefund however.
OL,18,FWhat's next for driving test changes?
