OL,3,CWhat are the changes being made to
OL,4,Cdriving tests?
OL,6,FMinister for the Future of Roads,
OL,7,FLilian Greenwood, said: "Driving is
OL,8,Fmore than just a means of transport;
OL,9,Fit is a lifeline for many.
OL,11,F"The measures announced today are
OL,12,Fanother vital step in tackling the
OL,13,Fdriving test backlog and ensuring that
OL,14,Fmore learners who are ready to take
OL,15,Ftheir test can do so without
OL,16,Funnecessary delays."
